# React Native Android App for Resume Analyzer

## Overview
This approach creates a native Android app using React Native that communicates with your Streamlit backend via API.

## Pros
- Native performance
- Offline capabilities
- Full device integration
- Smooth animations and transitions
- App store distribution

## Cons
- Requires React Native development
- Separate mobile codebase
- More complex than WebView

